Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 剛好十秒!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,再過會兒就得把田徑場讓給足球部了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,每人再跑一輪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊? 南高的倉田更新了百米個人最好成績
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,從跟腱斷裂的傷病中涅槃重生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喜屋武學姐 你知道她嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只不過我也是剛剛才知道她受了這個傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,跟腱的話 和橘學姐受的傷一樣吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,倉田在今天的縣大賽正賽出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道橘學姐的大賽記錄會不會被破…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不知怎的 看橘學姐就這樣告別田徑…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 就算是同樣的傷 每個人情況也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,別人能做得到的事 晶不可能做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,換地方!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 感覺要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這肯定得下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,應該還不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,田徑部收隊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&H3C3939&\bord0\pos(644.571,324.857)\u1}橘  11月值班意向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&H3C3939&\fs45\bord0\pos(522.286,495.142)}一、二、五、六
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&H3C3939&\bord0\pos(646.857,692.285)}（週日也沒問題）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐我們先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,退後!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道能不能撐到到車站為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐的足球部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs35\an7\c&HAEAEA7&\frz357.9\pos(459.81,42.381)}結果出來了!!!!\N南高倉田選手!\N100m\N更新個人最好成績!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,個人最好成績…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但和晶的成績比起來還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼都大驚小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,晶!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 晶!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.77,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs30\an7\c&H403D40&}結果出來了!!!!\N南高倉田選手!\N100m\N更新個人最好成績!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:38.77,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs30\an7\c&H403D40&\pos(10,140)}真的!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs30\an7\c&H403D40&\pos(10,179)}離大賽紀錄只差0.92秒!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs30\an7\c&H403D40&\pos(10,215)}真快!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,店長 再不走就要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,…嗯 等我打完這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這是下個月的值班意向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&H060202&\bord0\fs35\u1\pos(574.856,161.428)\frz336.7}橘  11月值班意向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&H060202&\bord0\fs35\frz336.7\pos(501.713,411.714)}一、二、五、六
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&H060202&\bord0\fs35\pos(457.142,539.714)\frz338.2}（週日也沒問題）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,啊? 週日也來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沒問題?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,橘你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,店長!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是總公司開會 你真的不能遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我晚上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 就不能提前一點出門嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩我們幾個也得加油幹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,665)}Time is money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,時間就是金錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,果然不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只好回到原點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨 請問幾位…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,空位置都能坐吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記了忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,…得快點了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,自助飲料一份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我馬上就走 不點別的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那還需要點單的話就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,和橘是同一款校服…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,回田徑部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,再這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你和田徑場…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,和我們也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,距離會越來越遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這太可悲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 取消點單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的正賽上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,刷新個人百米最好成績的那個倉田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她兩年前和你受了一樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直等你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍成電影了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:39.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准雅宋_GBK\bord1\fs35\an7\c&H151415&\3c&HD1E1F6&\b1}波起窗邊\N九條千尋\N\N{\fn微软雅黑\bord1\fs35\an7\c&H56DAE9&\3c&H0B3277&\b1}萬眾期待的\N電影化終於決定\N\N{\fn方正准雅宋_GBK\bord1\fs30\an7\c&HD4E6FA&\3c&H071D52&\b1}震撼心靈的故事，\N將在螢幕上再次詮釋感動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你的小說要拍成電影了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,話說你現在在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,剛散完步 現在快到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 真的誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想嚇你一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼有的沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你就算突然跑過來 我也一樣沒東西給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,房間裡也髒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼養了倉鼠?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,說來話長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 室內不許抽煙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天帶了好東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,鏘鏘!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,原來的那個碎了 我就買了個新的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要上網一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一點還行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可我們家沒咖啡豆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我又一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這也一點啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我買什麼都是一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,乞力馬扎羅咖啡和濾網!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,給大佬跪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,水要開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那差不多該就緒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…喂 東西拿出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,東西就是那東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,紙啊 稿紙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你該不會想來那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,對不對 小不點不點?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一個「不點」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快 拿出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找杯子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那我自己找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,傻瓜 不就在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 寫好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,「小鳥嘰嘰喳喳地問去哪」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,「帶來的到底是什麼種子?」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,「腳邊已不再傳來敲打的聲音」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,完全失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真是沒想到會在這裡寫一分鐘小說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,想起我們上學那會兒了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在咖啡落下之前寫不出短篇就得受罰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,現在想起來這簡直是個不得了的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,再說了虹吸式咖啡機出咖啡真的是一分鐘嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼知道 差不多就行了唄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來真是寫不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,當時就憑一股氣勢 出手便是文章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,明明根本沒有約好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可每天都期待得不得了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,後面其實也沒有什麼 可就是要全力爬上眼前的坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,等著吧 芥川!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我便是改變文壇潮流的中流砥柱!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真不明白當時怎麼有臉說這句話!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是俗話說的血氣方剛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,現在已經江郎才盡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而你在這方面就很厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,超級暢銷書作家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,作品居然還被拍成電影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那種小說就是獻媚大眾的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 你的作品確實拯救了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,文學根本不是救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,文學應該是毒藥!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不對嗎 近藤!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天來 該不會只是為了說這些話吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 我來是想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,…你好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你了解出道前的我 所以我想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦開始向前 就再也停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不允許失敗 只能向前衝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至不知道終點在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,忍受著周圍的期待的壓迫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,最後寫出一堆垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,為了自誡 我才來見你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我要找回曾經的那個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,千尋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才說不能再像原來那樣寫是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,其實並不是寫不出 而是不去寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得回不到原來的心境 就不該下筆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,否則 你就會對過去的自己失望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,擋你的路的 正是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,都一把年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能再回到當年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至還欠下一堆幼稚的感情無法解決的債
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但我由衷地把寫作當成我最神聖的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕只有一行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想用筆揮灑下劇毒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕只有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想用墨毒害他的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,…開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,其實 近藤你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,日子過得真是隨性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,和當年一樣 懷裡揣的還是初心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那房間裡裝著的 不是留戀 而是執念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那千尋 你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你抓住了僅有的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,正在挑戰文壇的更高峰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,和當年一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來你這裡視野真是差
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為看不見才刺激 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,執念嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 如果繼續保持初心…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,將來是不是就能到達理想的彼岸了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她兩年前和你受了一樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.34,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs25\an7\fad(294,0)\c&H6F6E6C&\frz20.29\pos(434,136.857)}結果出來了!!!!\N南高倉田選手!\N100m\N更新個人最好成績!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.55,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs35\an7\c&H9A8C81&\frz16.5\pos(360.857,333.428)}100m紀錄保持者是橘學姐吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.55,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs35\an7\c&H9A8C81&\frz16.5\pos(391.714,411.142)}是的，\N可是擔心會被超過啊!!\N再這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有人忘記東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這位顧客!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真的放棄離巢的燕子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就連仰望天空也會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,關於你上次給我的值班意向…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼上班真的沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就沒期中考試之類的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 我能來上班
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有了比打工更讓你感興趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,完全可以分出點時間來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 雖然店裡人手不太夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不是沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你學校裡總有別的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想幹別的!
